 《猪毁灭者》的布莱克·哈里森去世，享年 48 岁https://www.nme.com/news/music/pig-destroyers-blake-harrison-dies-age-48-3599635?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=pig-destroyers-blake-harrison-dies-age-48Anagricel Duran Mon, 11 Mar 2024 14:00:58 +0000 Music NewsNewsMetalPunk https://www.nme.com/?p=3599635 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们《猪毁灭者》永远感激能与他分享的时光。谢谢你所做的一切，布莱克”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/pig-destroyers-blake-harrison-dies-age-48-3599635">《Pig Destroyer》后的布莱克·哈里森 (Blake Harrison) 去世，享年 48 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="新媒体新闻" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/nme_news_tile-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>前 Pig Destroyer 主唱布莱克·哈里森 (Blake Harrison) 去世，享年 48 岁。</p><p>哈里森于 2006 年加入弗吉尼亚州亚历山大的 Grindcore 乐队担任主唱，并与他们一起演出直到 2022 年（根据<a href="https://blabbermouth.net/news/pig-destroyers-blake-harrison-dies" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Blabbermouth</em></a>报道）。他出现在乐队 2002 年的专辑《Phantom Limb》、2012 年的《Book Burner》和 2018 年的《Head Cage》中。截至撰写本文时，官方尚未公布死因。</p><p>乐队在他们的 Instagram 官方页面上确认了哈里森的去世，并向这位主唱致敬。 “20 多年来，Blake Hollingsworth Harrison 一直是我们的精神动物，”他们的帖子这样开头。 “在早期，布莱克的乐队 Daybreak 和 Pig Destroyer 都是刚刚起步的不满乐队，他们努力在音乐界留下自己的足迹。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4Whg8KNS2B/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,